description:
Check out all the places seen in this video: https://www.touropia.com/best-places-to-visit-in-italy/

Located in Southern Europe, this boot-shaped country is one of the worlds most popular travel destinations for a number of reasons that include art treasures, trendy fashion, stunning landscapes, passionate people and top-class cuisine. Italy offers so much to see and do that it would take a lifetime to explore.
